xvar='Age'
tab2=do.call(rbind,lapply(nfvar.list, function(x){
  eval(parse(text=paste('fit<-lm(scale(',x,')~ scale(',xvar,'),X1.dat %>% filter(is.na(',x,')==FALSE & is.na(',xvar,')==FALSE))')))
  tmp=summary(fit)$coefficients
  re=data.frame(yvar=x, xvar=xvar,beta=tmp[,1], CI95=confint(fit),pval=tmp[,4])
  rownames(re)<-NULL
  return(re[2,])
  }))  %>%
  mutate(p.adjust=p.adjust(pval,method='BH'))

      eval(parse(text=paste('nfdata2$chng.', j ,'= NA',sep='')))

}


do.call(rbind, lapply(networks,function(j){
    mycol=paste(c('task','rs'),j,sep='.')
    tmpdat = nfdata2[,c('Sub.ID',mycol)] %>% melt(.,id='Sub.ID')
    eval(parse(text=paste('fit=t.test(nfdata2$task.',j,',nfdata2$rs.',j,',paired=TRUE)',sep='')))
    eval(parse(text=paste('ds=effectsize::cohens_d(nfdata2$task.',j,',nfdata2$rs.',j,',paired=TRUE)',sep='')))
    
    a = (data.frame(networks=j,diff=fit$estimate,lci=fit$conf.int[1],uci=fit$conf.int[2],
               t=fit$statistic,df=fit$parameter,pvalue=fit$p.value,data.frame(ds)))
    return(a)
    })) %>%
  dplyr::select(-CI) %>%
  mutate(p.adjust=p.adjust(pvalue, method='BH')) %>% 
  mutate(sig = paste(ifelse(pvalue<0.05, 
                             ifelse(pvalue<0.01,

  • Variance comparison between resting and task
do.call(rbind, lapply(networks,function(j){
    mycol=paste(c('task','rs'),j,sep='.')
    tmpdat = nfdata2[,c('Sub.ID',mycol)] %>% 
      melt(.,id='Sub.ID') %>% 
      mutate(variable=factor(variable,levels=paste(c('rs','task'),j,sep='.')))
    vardesc=tmpdat %>% group_by(variable) %>% summarise(sd = sd(value)) %>% 
      mutate(variable=gsub(j,'',variable)) %>% reshape2::dcast(., .~variable,mean)
    fit=var.test(value ~ variable, tmpdat,alternative="two.sided")
    
    a = (data.frame(networks=j,vardesc,var.ratio = fit$estimate, ci=t(fit$conf.int),f=fit$statistic,df=t(fit$parameter),pvalue=fit$p.value))
    return(a)
    })) %>%
  mutate(p.adjust=p.adjust(pvalue, method='BH')) %>% 
  mutate(sig = paste(ifelse(pvalue<0.05, 
                             ifelse(pvalue<0.01, 
                                    ifelse(pvalue<0.001,'***','**'),'*'),''),
                     ifelse(p.adjust<0.05,'+',''),sep='')) %>%
  mutate(text=paste('[',round(ci.1,3),',',round(ci.2,3),']', sig))  %>%
  select(networks, rs., task., var.ratio,text)%>%
  kable(., digits=4) %>%
  kable_classic(.)

library(ggpubr)
sig_pairdtests2 <-function(nname){
  long = nfdata2[, c('Sub.ID','Age',paste('rs.',nname,sep=''),paste('task.',nname,sep=''))] %>%
    melt(.,id=c('Sub.ID','Age')) %>% rename(group=variable) %>%
    arrange(Sub.ID, group)
  
  re.table = long %>% 
    t_test(value ~ group, paired = TRUE) %>%
    mutate(.y.=nname) %>%
    add_significance() %>% data.frame(.)
  
  re.fig = ggplot(long, aes(x=group, y=value)) + 
    geom_line(aes(group=Sub.ID,colour=Age),alpha=0.5) + 
#    geom_point() +
    geom_boxplot(alpha=0.5) + 
    # scale_colour_gradientn(colours = rev(rainbow(10,end=0.7))) + 
    scale_colour_gradient(low = "yellow", high = "blue") +
    theme_economist_white(gray_bg = FALSE) +
    stat_compare_means(method = "t.test", paired=TRUE,
                       label.y = 0.17) + 
    ylab("NF") + xlab('') + 
    theme(legend.position="bottom", 
          legend.text=element_text(size=11)) + 
    scale_y_continuous(limits=c(0.05, 0.125), expand = c(0, 0)) + 
    scale_x_discrete(labels = c("Resting", "Task")) + 
    ggtitle(nname)
  
  return(list(re.table, re.fig) )
}


sig_nfvar.list = networks
sig_re = lapply(sig_nfvar.list, sig_pairdtests2)

do.call(rbind, lapply( 'Age', function(xvar){
do.call(rbind,lapply(networks.list, function(yvar){
  eval(parse(text=paste('fit<-lm(scale(',yvar,')~ scale(',xvar,'),nfdata2 %>% filter(is.na(',xvar,')==FALSE & is.na(',yvar,')==FALSE))')))
  tmp=summary(fit)$coefficients
  re=data.frame(xvar=xvar, yvar=yvar,beta=tmp[,1], CI95=confint(fit),pval=tmp[,4])
  rownames(re)<-NULL
  return(re[2,])
  }))}))  %>%
  mutate(p.adjust=p.adjust(pval,method='BH')) %>%
  mutate(sig = paste(ifelse(pval<0.05,ifelse(pval<0.01, ifelse(pval<0.001,'***','**'),'*'),''),
         ifelse(p.adjust<0.05,'+',''),sep='')) %>%
  filter(pval<0.1) %>%
  mutate(text = paste('[',round(CI95.2.5..,3), ',',round(CI95.97.5..,3),']',sig,sep='')) %>%
  dplyr::select(yvar,xvar, beta,pval,text) %>%
  kable(.,full=F,digit=3) %>%
  kable_classic(.)
